<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="144" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,737,1471,1790]" pageId="5" pageNumber="144">
Note. Since the type specimen of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Galiano" authorityYear="1965" box="[521,653,1473,1491]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Helvetia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="144" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="riojanensis">
<emphasis box="[521,653,1473,1491]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="144">H. riojanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
has not been examined, the identification and diagnosis of this species is based on the illustrations and description by 
<bibRefCitation author="GALIANO" firstAuthor="GALIANO" journalOrPublisher="Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina" pageId="5" pageNumber="144" pagination="47 - 50" part="27" refId="ref6489" refString="GALIANO, M. E. 1965. Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae). Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina 27: 47 - 50." title="Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae)" type="journal article" year="1965">GALIANO (1965)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="144" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="5.[113,737,1471,1790]" pageId="5" pageNumber="144">
Diagnosis. Males of this species are very similar to those of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Gustavo R. S. Ruiz &amp; Antonio D. Brescovit" authorityYear="2008" box="[141,261,1621,1641]" class="Arachnida" family="Salticidae" genus="Helvetia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="5" pageNumber="144" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="galianoae">
<emphasis box="[141,157,1622,1640]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="144">H</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[171,261,1621,1640]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="144">galianoae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by the shape of the RTA, from which they can be distinguished by having a stout cymbium seen in ventral view and longer RTA branches (see 
<bibRefCitation author="GALIANO" box="[465,599,1680,1700]" firstAuthor="GALIANO" journalOrPublisher="Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina" pageId="5" pageNumber="144" pagination="47 - 50" part="27" refId="ref6489" refString="GALIANO, M. E. 1965. Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae). Revista de la Socieda d Entomologica Argentina 27: 47 - 50." title="Descripcion de Helvetia riojanensis sp. n. y del alotipo ♂ de H. al bovittata Simon (A raneae, Salticidae)" type="journal article" year="1965">GALIANO 1965</bibRefCitation>
, figs 1 and 3).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
